        "河水齐腰深"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "齊"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "adverb",
      "meaning": "同时，同样，一起",
      "examples": [
        "齐名",
        "齐声",
        "齐心协力",
        "一齐前进"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "齊"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "adjective",
      "meaning": "全，完全",
      "examples": [
        "齐全",
        "人到齐了"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "齊"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "中国周代诸侯国名，疆域在今山东、河北部分地区",
      "examples": [
