        "北朝齐"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "齊"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "调剂，调和（后作“剂”）",
      "examples": [
        "齐药",
        "处齐不过数种"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "齊"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "药剂（后作“剂”）",
      "examples": [
        "取齐",
        "服齐"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "齊"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "界限，分际",
      "examples": [
